48a978" class="r-1wafrbo" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="6d9ab33c-d8a2-4b36-b2b8-e69df549c1c9" class="r-12jzekq"><div data-rid="0f103697-1ef9-4a56-8c5a-dc5d962a0182" class="r-1ist793 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</p></span></div><div data-rid="02b20e2e-abba-4a68-8cb5-27b981c338ce" class="r-nov30l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>We offer a guarantee on all products purchased directly from Arccos Golf!</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="747ff277-87fb-4331-9887-d91acecac06a" class="r-dmua7m" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="77f2491c-5621-4e56-9d83-a14e948d11d8" class="r-1gpt3a9" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="608c0edd-31ad-4ee5-8f5a-707cae2fbe38" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rclur2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1w8qfc9"><div data-rid="54346748-70be-4924-b619-0d4522483d1b" class="r-pgxkxt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Product Description</p></span></div><div data-rid="eb2eb035-945c-4316-94dd-fb8ccf20f2ed" class="r-1s4787c" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-y89dx" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rclur2:"><div data-rid="2b9f224f-c0f4-46a2-9e63-e0bc1aaadb7b" class="r-1qd2bqs"><div data-rid="9564628f-2072-4c5e-ad6b-256015e5a5ea" class="r-1orp99l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Arccos Air is a compact wearable that clips to your belt or slides in your pocket. Built-in motion sensors and GPS detect every shot automatically, powered by AI trained on 1.5 billion+ real golf shots. No sensors on your clubs. No phone required. Just play your round while Arccos captures everything in the background.</p><p><br></p><p>Your purchase includes the Arccos Air wearable, a charging case, and one year of Arccos Game Tracking Membership with full access to the Arccos app, including Strokes Gained Analytics, Smart Club Distances, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and more.</p><p><br></p><p>Compatible with iOS, Android coming soon. Works with or without Smart Sensors.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b1ad21f3-acc7-4168-b395-82700fda4038" class="r-1jypb8l" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="b99c25f8-a6fa-4b02-bb8b-63bbc504f777" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rklur2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-12dws9m"><div data-rid="3cd7f280-b8f7-45ff-828e-c70ed903ea12" class="r-jn6b37 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Shipping + Return Policy</p></span></div><div data-rid="b8a7cbc9-d0d8-473b-95cf-2d6028a66816" class="r-1vdzzvv" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-8k7wdw" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rklur2:"><div data-rid="6de337cd-5118-49f2-98f4-0af87c960125" class="r-1j7e9dw"><div data-rid="b1a1f5d5-c5e3-4132-9122-319e91b53ad5" class="r-1eynqdm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Orders typically ship within 1-2 business days. Estimated delivery dates are provided at checkout based on your location.</p><br><p>All Arccos products come with a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied, you can return your product within 30 days of delivery. Customer is responsible for return shipping costs.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="63f9f85e-9853-43bf-be87-eba8d1ff3815" class="r-ytad72" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="6c6b975c-1e82-4d0e-8dac-7b8fadc6f0f7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rslur2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-anfxr3"><div data-rid="92ba8558-86f4-47e9-993a-9db093424a74" class="r-1d48xi1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need sensors on my clubs?</p></span></div><div data-rid="48da997d-9247-44b8-ad56-5248face706a" class="r-14yk812" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-ihcrsb" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rslur2:"><div data-rid="5ca4f1ae-7f1b-4a7b-8832-e3094b7c7658" class="r-nllyai"><div data-rid="fc7a5823-0dc3-45ba-9094-d2ea6f203767" class="r-g2jfdb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No, that's now optional. Arccos Air tracks your game automatically without any sensors on your clubs. Every shot is detected by the wearable. Just play. You get full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and scoring insights. For the deepest club-level insights, many members prefer to also use Smart Sensors — but they're completely optional.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d5f93169-d967-4b0c-ad1f-1c1ff9a6056e" class="r-jluagu" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="365beca1-f2cd-4616-8715-f3fb6fae7c74" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R14lur2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1c4ox7s"><div data-rid="10058212-92e7-4068-ac3d-b86b172836e3" class="r-jijetb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need to carry my phone?</p></span></div><div data-rid="311b6bde-f69c-4744-bb78-81e6288d0c71" class="r-kjpr2n" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1af386l" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R14lur2:"><div data-rid="c954726a-b3b5-4421-9fbd-5c386accc4b7" class="r-19q984j"><div data-rid="31d7f695-1e9a-44c8-8152-01205a4749f3" class="r-h0868b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No. That's one of the biggest differences with Arccos Air. The wearable replaces the need for your phone or an Apple Watch on the course. Just slip Air in your pocket, or clip it on your belt and play. Your shot data syncs to the app after your round or whenever you're back in range.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="90862ff7-cdbf-4507-b0f3-534dae338166" class="r-1sen4lj" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d91ca41a-7c73-491f-b412-e008d69ea127" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1clur2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-d3ni9n"><div data-rid="f7a053de-e6df-430e-a46f-8053407a5437" class="r-1g2j4qy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How accurate is the shot tracking?</p></span></div><div data-rid="801f3d47-6f30-4685-b2da-21a33af44b34" class="r-1qrg13t" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-9xeerv" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"><